quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,8,ae hamaray perwar-digaar un ko hamesha rehne ke bahishtoon mein daakhil kar jin ka tunay un se wadakiya hai aur jo un ke baap dada aur un ki biwion aur un ki aulaad mein se naik hon un ko bhi. be shak to ghalib hikmat wala hai
  40,9,aur un ko azabon se bachaaye rakh. aur jis ko to is roz azabon se bacha le ga to be shak is par meharbani farmai aur yahi barri kamyabi hai
  40,10,jin logon ne kufarkiya un se pukaar kar keh diya jaye ga ke jab tum ( duniya mein ) imaan ki taraf bulaye jatay they aur mantay nahi they to khuda is se kahin ziyada bezaar hota tha jis qader tum apne aap se bezaar ho rahay ho
  40,11,woh kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne hum ko do dafaa be jaankiya aur do dafaa jaan bakhsh. hum ko apne gunaaho ka iqraar hai tokiya niklny ki koi Sabeel hai ?
  40,12,yeh is liye ke jab tanha khuda ko puraka jata tha to tum inkaar kardete they. aur agar is ke sath shareek muqarrarkiya jata tha to tasleem kar lete they to hukum to khuda hi ka hai jo ( sab se ) oopar aur ( sab se ) bara hai
  40,13,wohi to hai jo tum ko apni nishanain dekhata hai aur tum par aasman se rizaq utaarta hai. aur nasiyaat to wohi pokarta hai jo ( is ki taraf ) rujoo karta hai
  40,14,to khuda ki ibadat ko khalis kar kar usi ko poukaro agarchay kafir bura hi manen
  40,15,maalik darjaat aali aur sahib arsh hai. apne bundon mein se jis par chahta hai apne hukum se wahi bhejta hai taakay mulaqaat ke din se draway
  40,16,jis roz woh nikal parrin ge un ki koi cheez khuda se makhfi nah rahay gi. aaj kis ki badshahat hai? khuda ki jo akela aur ghalib hai
